flourishing, how-to culture

00:25:06.400 --> 00:25:11.440
of conferences and gurus
telling us to get out there.

00:25:11.440 --> 00:25:14.140
And so to me, it's actually
a little confusing.

00:25:14.140 --> 00:25:16.840
You know, should I
be a great networker

00:25:16.840 --> 00:25:19.700
or should I just
pursue my own passion?

00:25:19.700 --> 00:25:21.669
I think the answer is
pursue your own passion

00:25:21.669 --> 00:25:22.960
and you'll figure it out later.

00:25:22.960 --> 00:25:24.820
If you're good enough
at what you do,

00:25:24.820 --> 00:25:27.430
