00:28:40.530 --> 00:28:43.050
And it feels like there
are these very big channels

00:28:43.050 --> 00:28:45.600
of being connected,
interacting with people,

00:28:45.600 --> 00:28:48.330
having influence, blah
blah blah, that I'm not

00:28:48.330 --> 00:28:50.250
participating in
