00:28:52.770 --> 00:28:54.660
to participate in those.

00:28:54.660 --> 00:28:57.200
Do you have any
thoughts or suggestions?

00:28:57.200 --> 00:28:59.880
MORRA AARONS-MELE: I just
want to say I hear you.

00:28:59.880 --> 00:29:01.680
I feel the same.

00:29:01.680 --> 00:29:04.170
I feel sometimes that
participating online

00:29:04.170 --> 00:29:10.650
is almost more of a
challenge and that you

00:29:10.650 --> 00:29:12.270
do have to force yourself.

00:29:12.270 --> 00:29:16.330
