00:29:20.440 --> 00:29:21.700
I should be gaining influence.

00:29:21.700 --> 00:29:24.490
I should be building
my personal brand.

00:29:24.490 --> 00:29:25.780
My question is, why?

00:29:25.780 --> 00:29:27.436
DAVID: FOMO-- Fear
Of Missing Out.

00:29:27.436 --> 00:29:29.060
MORRA AARONS-MELE:
Fear Of Missing Out.

00:29:29.060 --> 00:29:31.030
So that's my question to you.

00:29:31.030 --> 00:29:33.820
What's your motivation for
building the influence?

00:29:33.820 --> 00:29:37.990
And then, OK, I want to write.

00:29:37.990 --> 00:29:41.590
Do you want to make a
creative contribution?

00:29:41.590 --> 00:29:44.860
Do you want to grow your network
for potential future career

00:29:44.860 --> 00:29:46.090
opportunities?

00:29:46.090 --> 00:29:48.580
Do you just want to build
your online landscape,

00:29:48.580 --> 00:29:52.100
your online footprint,
your online profile?

00:29:52.100 --> 00:29:54.616
Maybe pick one simple way.

00:29:54.616 --> 00:29:55.990
For me, it's always
been writing.

00:29:55.990 --> 00:29:57.250
I'm comfortable writing.

00:29:57.250 --> 00:29:58.510
I like to write.

