the other parts of social media

00:30:04.450 --> 00:30:06.730
that made me feel naked.

00:30:06.730 --> 00:30:09.010
I think that there
are ways to build

00:30:09.010 --> 00:30:11.590
your online footprint that
are less social, but equally

00:30:11.590 --> 00:30:13.240
legit--

00:30:13.240 --> 00:30:16.750
photography, video,
recipes, writing.

00:30:16.750 --> 00:30:17.750
So maybe start there.

00:30:17.750 --> 00:30:20.920
But I think it's
also OK to say, why?

00:30:20.920 --> 00:30:23.772
Who says I have to
do this right now?

00:30:23.772 --> 00:30:25.974
And like, baby steps.

00:30:25.974 --> 00:30:28.317
AUDIENCE: Hey,
thanks for coming.

