This is where conferences
actually can be very helpful.

00:31:06.590 --> 00:31:09.660
And because she does want to get
into a very specific industry,

00:31:09.660 --> 00:31:12.170
I mean, I would encourage her
to even go a little bit deeper

00:31:12.170 --> 00:31:12.920
than animation.

00:31:12.920 --> 00:31:13.970
You know, is there
a certain area?

00:31:13.970 --> 00:31:14.990
Does she want to
do entertainment?

00:31:14.990 --> 00:31:15.980
Does she want to do scientific?

00:31:15.980 --> 00:31:17.230
Does she want to do technical?

00:31:17.230 --> 00:31:17.780
I don't know.

00:31:17.780 --> 00:31:19.760
But what I would
do-- honestly, this

00:31:19.760 --> 00:31:22.550
