would start on Twitter

00:31:22.550 --> 00:31:25.040
and use some search
term, seeking.

00:31:25.040 --> 00:31:26.420
And find out who's writing--

00:31:26.420 --> 00:31:27.961
this is what I would
tell my clients,

00:31:27.961 --> 00:31:29.240
too-- who's writing about it?

00:31:29.240 --> 00:31:30.580
Are there animators tweeting?

00:31:30.580 --> 00:31:34.160
Who are people on YouTube
who have big followings?

00:31:34.160 --> 00:31:35.690
I would start following them.

00:31:35.690 --> 00:31:38.960
And I would figure out what
are the publications they site

00:31:38.960 --> 00:31:40.610
or contribute to--

00:31:40.610 --> 00:31:43.340
message boards, websites--
and is there a conference they

00:31:43.340 --> 00:31:44.330
go to.

00:31:44.330 --> 00:31:45.560
Honestly.

00:31:45.560 --> 00:31:48.830
And then she needs to
have a battle plan.

00:31:48.830 --> 00:31:50.480
I would challenge her.

00:31:50.480 --> 00:31:53.384
If there's a conference in LA,
for example, where she says,

00:31:53.384 --> 00:31:55.550
you know, potential employers
are going to be there.

00:31:55.550 --> 00:31:59.300
This person that I really
want to work for is speaking.

00:31:59.300 --> 00:32:01.640
That's the place where
she's got to have her plan,

00:32:01.640 --> 00:32:05.969
and she's got to figure out her
online strategy ahead of time.

00:32:05.969 --> 00:32:07.010
She's got a good website.

00:32:07.010 --> 00:32:08.134
She's got a good portfolio.

00:32:08.134 --> 00:32:10.610
Is she following the
right people on Twitter?

00:32:10.610 --> 00:32:13.460
Go to the conference,
have a strategy,

00:32:13.460 --> 00:32:15.980
try to meet five people.

00:32:15.980 --> 00:32:18.260
Maybe she can bring
an extrovert with her.

00:32:18.260 --> 00:32:19.130
And do it.

00:32:19.130 --> 00:32:21.140
Because when you are
going to break in,

00:32:21.140 --> 00:32:22.930
you sometimes have
to get out there.

00:32:22.930 --> 00:32:24.740
And sometimes the face
time of a conference

00:32:24.740 --> 00:32:26.420
is actually really great.

00:32:26.420 --> 00:32:27.362
It just is.

